{"tid":675003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點評兩任主席 發叔對梁君彥「有保留」","createTime":"2018-05-23T07:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T08:35:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47ac2b39cf2011ccd89a8ca4dd22fc73ffe71a04","tid":675003,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398925&d=c%2BJMtgH2msu1T9K6ZL12azCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5e246ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398925&h=42076383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398925</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：點評兩任主席<br />\n發叔對梁君彥「有保留」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180523/large/a12a02a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180523%2Flarge%2Fa12a02a.gif&h=426b23a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■發叔日前同咖喱范（右）及何民傑（左）大談政事。范國威fb圖片<br />\n <br />\n新同盟范國威日前約咗前立法局主席黃宏發同佢嘅愛徒西貢區議員何民傑一齊去布袋澳食海鮮。唔明呢個飯腳組合？咖喱范解釋，何民傑曾喺3.11為佢助選，但對方出席唔到慰勞宴，直至前日先約到，索性叫對方約埋黃宏發一齊擦番餐。<br />\n<br />\n咖喱范話發叔當年任議員時為過布袋澳村民搞污水牌問題，村民對佢感情好深，食肆仲會為發叔炮製獨家美食。咖喱范話席間由修改《議事規則》後嘅立法會運作，傾到梁君彥主持會議嘅質素，再由政治哲學談到香港政治嘅第三條路線，指發叔依舊思路敏捷。<br />\n<br />\n咁發叔對梁君彥主持會議有何評價？咖喱范引述對方「有保留」，其間亦對歷任主席點評一番，以財政預算案議員修訂案為例指，自己唔會似曾鈺成咁寬鬆批幾百個，亦唔會似梁君彥收窄到幾十項，強調主席主持會議要夠「體統」，並協助解決各種衝突。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：有任務！小肥張帶傷報國 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：地獄廚神麥美娟「得道」靠佛祖 (李八方)"},{"pid":"964d08a90c0738d49b930403e314d7654fd03048","tid":675003,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af8be7b6d7bc9e80346c247e0bea35d0d6ebab19","tid":675003,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6df452acc5dd14cae1937a5a3c923a858afda8ca","tid":675003,"uid":56157,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"佢又叫發叔？我以為發叔講緊死左嗰個。<br />\n嚇到我，以為佢翻生"},{"pid":"770e0e057b8b1ad414c7a421cd02cbd388ba5126","tid":675003,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"964d08a90c0738d49b930403e314d7654fd03048","tid":675003,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"條友公正只不過係因為03年前 <br />\n所謂密月期<br />\n<br />\n中共扮野 無咁明目張膽搞香港<br />\n<br />\n講公平 老鼠成應該都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adba1e948951f2c17d030f5bdab53c4162f2decf","tid":675003,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770e0e057b8b1ad414c7a421cd02cbd388ba5126","tid":675003,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"964d08a90c0738d49b930403e314d7654fd03048","tid":675003,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"條友公正只不過係因為03年前 <br />\n所謂密月期<br />\n<br />\n中共扮野 無咁明目張膽搞香港<br />\n<br />\n講公平 老鼠成應該都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"我話梁耀宗最公平"}]}